      <p>
        <s>The text out of the fourth scene of the theatre <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="title">Disgraced, Scene 4</ref> <choice><orig>wich</orig><reg>which</reg></choice> was <choice><orig>writen</orig><reg>written</reg></choice> by <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="author">Ayad Akhtar</ref> is about <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character"><choice><orig>Abes</orig><reg>Abe's</reg></choice></ref> current situation and his uncle <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Amir</ref> trying to help him out.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>In the first part <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="line">(l. 1-19)</ref> <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Abe</ref> tells <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Emily</ref> and <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Amir</ref>, that his immigration status has been brought up and that it is up for renewal.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>In the following <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="line">(l. 16-39)</ref> <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Amir</ref> calls <choice><orig>a</orig><reg>an</reg></choice> attorney who can help <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Abe</ref> in this situation.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>The third scene-part is about <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Abe</ref> getting deported back to <name type="geo">Pakistan</name> where <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Amir</ref> says the life is worse <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="line">(l. 36-45)</ref>.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>After that <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="line">(l. 46-54)</ref> <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Amir</ref> wants <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Abe</ref> to play him more respect, but <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Abe</ref> says, that he is just speaking the truth.</s>
      </p>
      <p>
        <s>In the last part <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="line">(l. 60-75)</ref> <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Amir</ref> disrespects <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Abe</ref>, in the following <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Abe</ref> tells <ref target="a11lk1_1" type="character">Amir</ref> that he will handle it himself.</s>
      </p>
